A NOTE ABOUT TADS, THE TEXT ADVENTURE DEVELOPMENT SYSTEM

Dungeon was implemented with the Text Adventure Development System, or TADS,
which is a programming tool designed for writing text adventures.  TADS
is available as "shareware," so you may be able to obtain TADS from the same
place as this Dungeon program.  TADS is a High Energy Software product.

